    "The AWS Management Console is a web-based interface provided by Amazon Web Services (AWS) that allows users to access and manage their AWS resources. It provides a graphical user interface (GUI) for interacting with various AWS services, making it easier for users to configure, monitor, and deploy resources in the AWS cloud.\n",
    "\n"
